Prostatic \Pro*stat"ic\, a. (Anat.) Of or pertaining to the prostate gland. [1913 Webster]
{Prostatic catheter}. (Med.) See under {Catheter}. [1913 Webster]
prostatic adj : relating to the prostate gland [syn: {prostate}]
